Offices.Name: Hertz - Amsterdam Schiphol airport
Offices.Description: Car Rental Centre (Arrivals Hall 3 (Car Rental Area))

Offices.Name: Green Motion - Amsterdam Schiphol airport
Offices.Description: Shuttle Service (Follow the signs “Buses and Hotel Shuttles”. In Arrival hall 3, take the Exit C. Once outside turn right, in approximately 50 meters you will reach bus stop “Airport Hotel shuttle 15”. At this bus stop 15, take the Shuttle Bus named "Quick Parking Shuttle" which will bring you to the Rental Station. Tel: 0031(0)85 485 73 20 for any inquiries)

Offices.Name: Goldcar - Amsterdam Schiphol airport
Offices.Description: Shuttle Service (Follow the 'Hotel Shuttle' signs to Arrivals 3, then follow directions to take the Hotel Shuttle from bus stop C13. The bus will take you to the Goldcar office at the 'Corendon Village Hotel'. Call 0031202142034 if you require assistance.)
